org.friendlysnmp.mib

Class RowStatusTC

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.friendlysnmp.mib.RowStatusTC

  • public class RowStatusTC
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class to use RowStatus integer values. It cannot be converted to enum because its values are converted by FConverter from Integer to org.snmp4j.smi.Variable object. Fields spelling and comments are from RFC-2579 SNMPv2-TC MIB.
